Package: libbitcoin-explorer-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libbitcoin-explorer (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Asynchronous C++ Bitcoin library - development files
 libbitcoin-explorer is a Bitcoin command line tool.
 .
 This package provides the development files (ie. includes, static library),
 that allow to build software which uses libbitcoin-explorer.

